WEBVTT

00:00:00.285 --> 00:00:04.859
.. INTERVIEW, kasete numer tsvey, bit dertseyln zi vayter.

00:00:07.124 --> 00:00:07.958
in

00:00:08.747 --> 00:00:11.410
vi ikh hob gezogt frier hobn hobn undzere eygene mentshn,

00:00:12.278 --> 00:00:16.236
heymishe yinglekh, geyogt eyner dem andern men zol vi shneler fartik vern.

00:00:16.236 --> 00:00:21.279
m'iz take fartik gevorn tsu zibn ober, zibn vokhn mit epes

00:00:21.537 --> 00:00:25.602
biz, vi mir ho'mir etlekhe mentshn gezen UNK az

00:00:25.720 --> 00:00:27.720
s'iz nisht keyn rede men zol undz aheymlozn,

00:00:27.849 --> 00:00:30.419
aderabe, men hot undz gegebn nokh shverer arbet.

00:00:32.440 --> 00:00:33.655
un ze'mir dort geven

00:00:33.784 --> 00:00:36.967
shtots, dray khadoshim ze'mir sort geven

00:00:37.107 --> 00:00:39.322
bald zeks, iber zeks khadoshim.

00:00:40.053 --> 00:00:43.569
azoy vayt az di, m- undzere familye

00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:47.505
hot nisht gevust, men hot nisht getort hobn keyn shum min kontakt mit di mishpokhe.

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.580
men hot nisht a mol, gevust keyner vu undz gefin mir zikh, ze'mir in oysland? ze'mir in Rusnland?

00:00:52.784 --> 00:00:54.516
ze'mir in di medine? men hot nisht gevust.

00:00:55.599 --> 00:00:57.406
s'hot zikh per tsufal getrofn dort,

00:00:57.454 --> 00:01:02.016
s'iz geven a toytfal oykh eyner, dos, bay der arbet dort, hot zikh getrofn epes aza umglik fal dort,

00:01:03.147 --> 00:01:06.964
azoy men hot epes gehert in di heym az s'iz epes zeyer nisht foderik di zakhn mit undz.

00:01:10.644 --> 00:01:15.753
endlekh, nokh iber zeks khadoshim,

00:01:18.164 --> 00:01:19.478
un mit groyse mi, hobn mir

00:01:20.084 --> 00:01:24.313
nisht gehat keyn e-, men hot undz nisht gegebn tsu esn genug, ze'mir geven opgeshvakht ale, mir hobn koym mir gekent geyn,

00:01:25.318 --> 00:01:26.221
ze'mir ongekumen aheym.

00:01:31.513 --> 00:01:32.690
hob ikh mir forgenumen,

00:01:33.844 --> 00:01:35.981
ikh un nokh etlekhe fun undz,

00:01:36.427 --> 00:01:37.330
hobn mir zikh forgenumen,

00:01:40.141 --> 00:01:41.741
ikh hob gehat zeyer, zeyer a gutn khaver,

00:01:43.124 --> 00:01:44.541
MAYBE ir hot im gekent efsher,

00:01:46.438 --> 00:01:50.747
do in di Dizengof hot er gehat a PICTURE gesheft, Royznfeld Loran,

00:01:51.421 --> 00:01:52.073
Royznfeld.

00:01:53.078 --> 00:01:54.964
eyner fun di greste PICTURES gesheftn do

00:01:55.318 --> 00:01:56.861
in Dizengof, er iz nebekh far a yor geshtorbn.

00:01:57.431 --> 00:01:59.958
er iz geven eyner fun di beste khaveyrim mayne.

00:02:03.501 --> 00:02:04.656
er hot zikh oykh forgenumen

00:02:05.216 --> 00:02:07.673
azoy vi ikh, az mir veln mir aheymgeyn

00:02:08.788 --> 00:02:09.260
veln mir zikh

00:02:09.867 --> 00:02:15.483
ober farshafn andere shriftn, ober men vet m'vet zikh epes erleydikn, m'zol nisht darfn nokh a mol onkumen in keyn

00:02:15.483 --> 00:02:17.870
arbayts lager, undz ho'mir zikh antshlosn

00:02:17.870 --> 00:02:20.612
az mer veln mir undz nisht geyn in keyn arbayts lager.

00:02:20.645 --> 00:02:22.516
men ken nisht gleybn dey may- khevre,

00:02:22.661 --> 00:02:24.935
az zey zogn draysik tog, dos ken zayn

00:02:24.987 --> 00:02:26.806
Rusnland ken dos zayn, un andere zakhn,

00:02:28.919 --> 00:02:30.806
in tsvishn,

00:02:30.919 --> 00:02:34.370
hob ikh gehat a bakantn ENGINEER, eyner dokter Merkzamer,

00:02:35.016 --> 00:02:40.193
er iz geven a mer a yedid mit mayn tatn olevasholem, s'iz geven shoyn a zakh fun fertsik fuftsik yor alt,

00:02:41.435 --> 00:02:43.483
hot er gezogt er hot farbindung,

00:02:43.548 --> 00:02:47.684
in Budapest iz geven a gants fabrik, zey hobn gemakht motorn,

00:02:47.915 --> 00:02:53.112
hobn gearbet, ikh veys nisht efsher fuftsik tsi hundert toyznt mentshn dort, eyns eyns fun di greste fabrikn in Ungarn.

00:02:53.169 --> 00:02:54.427
in Budapest iz dos geven.

00:02:56.290 --> 00:02:59.604
dort iz geven, azolkhe

00:02:59.924 --> 00:03:01.421
arbayter vos zey hobn gearbet

00:03:02.198 --> 00:03:04.438
⟨HODGYU ZEMPS⟩ se hot geheysn men hot gearbet farn

00:03:05.273 --> 00:03:06.656
far di milkhome hot men gearbet.

00:03:07.547 --> 00:03:09.225
un di hobn nisht gedarft aynrukn.

00:03:09.356 --> 00:03:11.948
deye mentshn vos hobn gearbet in azelkhe fabrikn,

00:03:12.416 --> 00:03:14.198
vos zey hobn gearbet far far di milkhome,

00:03:14.485 --> 00:03:16.197
dey hobn nisht gedarft aynrukn.

00:03:19.284 --> 00:03:20.850
un der dokter Merkzamer

00:03:21.376 --> 00:03:22.381
hot gezogt far mayn tate

00:03:22.633 --> 00:03:23.307
ikh gedenk nisht far

00:03:23.947 --> 00:03:26.438
tsen tsi iber tsvontsik toyznt, tsvontsik toyznt PENGO

00:03:26.804 --> 00:03:31.044
oyser dem yedn khoydesh, ikh veys nisht, tsvey ober dray toyznt PENGO a khoydesh,

00:03:31.776 --> 00:03:33.764
ken men erleydikn men zol onkumen ahin oyf,

00:03:34.918 --> 00:03:38.347
arbaytn, men darf nisht arbetn ober men zol mir dort figurirn az m'arbet mir dort,

00:03:39.501 --> 00:03:42.061
un men vet nisht darfn aynrukn. dey Gants GYAR iz geven a,

00:03:42.827 --> 00:03:47.021
eyns fun di greste krigs fabrikn vos men hot gearbet krig zakhn.

00:03:47.359 --> 00:03:50.016
ho'mir geklert fun dem iz shoyn keyn shtarker's nishto.

00:03:54.141 --> 00:03:57.878
endlekh, s'iz durkhgegan efsher finf zeks vokhn, mir ho'mir gemeynt az dos iz gut.

00:04:00.801 --> 00:04:03.828
ho'mir vider bakumen an aynruf tsetl.

00:04:06.984 --> 00:04:08.763
undz ho'mir balangt,

00:04:09.558 --> 00:04:12.044
s'iz geven a shtot zekhtsik kilometer dort fun undz,

00:04:12.127 --> 00:04:15.157
NAGYBANYA. NAGYBANYA.

00:04:15.467 --> 00:04:18.130
dort iz geven an oyberleytenant, der komendant eyner POLGAR.

00:04:19.433 --> 00:04:20.736
der hot gehat aza zikorn,

00:04:21.387 --> 00:04:24.496
se flegn durkhgeyn tsen toyznter, tsu hundert toyznter mentshn unter zayn hant,

00:04:25.410 --> 00:04:27.158
ober der hot aza zikorn gehat gedenkt

00:04:27.410 --> 00:04:30.050
mamesh yede mentsh, er iz geven epes a zhe- a zheni!

00:04:34.450 --> 00:04:35.604
ikh hob bakumen dos aynruf tsetl,

00:04:38.210 --> 00:04:41.261
ze'mir aribergeforn keyn, mit dem inzhenier in eynem,

00:04:42.644 --> 00:04:43.490
keyn Budapest,

00:04:44.496 --> 00:04:47.924
bay nakht nokh dem der ershter tsu fri UNK.

00:04:47.955 --> 00:04:51.147
ze'mir arayngegan tsu dem ofitsir

00:04:51.627 --> 00:04:55.158
vos er iz geven a a mayor iz er geven fun di Gants fabrik,

00:04:57.844 --> 00:04:58.827
zogt er, "her mikh tsu," zogt er

00:05:00.324 --> 00:05:02.793
"leyder ken ikh gornisht tun. far vos?"

00:05:03.958 --> 00:05:06.656
zogt er, "vayl der oyberleytenant fun NAGYBANYA, der POLGAR,

00:05:07.684 --> 00:05:11.433
hot telefonirt," zogt er, "az Adalbert Frid

00:05:12.713 --> 00:05:17.764
ken nisht zayn bay nakht keyn arbayter," zogt er, "er iz geven in in lager," zogt er, "der iz nisht keyn fakhman nisht a mol,

00:05:18.381 --> 00:05:23.901
er hot nisht gekent, "zogt er, "vern iber nakht a COAL, veys ikh, aza koyln arbayter, ikh veys," zogt er.

00:05:23.901 --> 00:05:26.028
hot er ongezogt far dem mayor dort,

00:05:26.028 --> 00:05:30.141
"zolst zogn im, ikh eytse im az er zol zofort arayn- aynrukn,

00:05:30.507 --> 00:05:32.934
tomer vet er nisht aynrukn veln ikh im lozn arestirn, ikh vel im shteln

00:05:32.934 --> 00:05:34.221
tsum krigs-gerikht!"

00:05:39.673 --> 00:05:42.450
der khaver, ze'mir aheymgekumen,

00:05:42.556 --> 00:05:43.958
undz ho'mir gezen se iz nisht do vos tsu tun do.

00:05:44.389 --> 00:05:51.916
der khaver, der Lo- Royznfeld, Loran vos er iz far a yor geshtorbn,

00:05:54.058 --> 00:05:58.190
far a yor geshtorbn,

00:05:58.619 --> 00:06:00.523
iz,

00:06:01.273 --> 00:06:06.073
zayn shvoger geven epes arestirt demolts, er hot gedint, zogt er, "her tsi, ikh hob nisht keyn

00:06:06.621 --> 00:06:09.524
oyshaltung ikh zol kenen koyfn andere shriftn,

00:06:10.998 --> 00:06:13.273
un, ikh ruk ayn.

00:06:14.130 --> 00:06:15.437
du tu vi azoy du farshteyst."

00:06:18.038 --> 00:06:20.404
dos aynruf tsetl hot er geloytet keyn Oroshaza.

00:06:23.238 --> 00:06:27.768
dos iz loy- dos iz loytn, dos iz Ungarn.

00:06:27.886 --> 00:06:32.576
dos iz geven le- lebn BEKESCABA, an ungarishe shtot, an ungarishe shtot,

00:06:32.775 --> 00:06:40.786
der hot ayngerukt, der khaver mayn, hot er gezogt az er vet epes kenen erleydikn vet er zofort shikn a telegram, ober er vet mikh onrufn telefonish.

00:06:41.983 --> 00:06:46.050
endlekh dem andern tog, tsi tsvey tog deroyf, bakum ikh a telegram

00:06:47.158 --> 00:06:50.027
er get mir an adrese ikh zol forn keyn BEKESCABA

00:06:51.193 --> 00:06:53.844
un ikh zol oyfrufn, tsugeyn in di un di gas,

00:06:54.130 --> 00:06:57.434
ikh zol oyf- oyfzukhn a meydl dort, eyne Magda vi zi heyst

00:06:57.867 --> 00:06:59.878
di hot farbindungen un di vet kenen erleydikn

00:07:00.998 --> 00:07:01.673
ikh zol nisht darfn aynrukn.

00:07:06.336 --> 00:07:10.930
dem Royznfeld's a shvester, der man iz geven arestirt in Segedin, iz oykh gekumen,

00:07:11.037 --> 00:07:14.488
hot oykh gevolt zen vos men ken erleydikn, un in eyn vegs iz zi geforn tsum man

00:07:14.724 --> 00:07:15.851
bazukhn dem man.

00:07:17.691 --> 00:07:20.641
ikh bin ongekumen ahin keyn BEKESCABA, zog ikh farn

00:07:20.641 --> 00:07:22.839
fyaker, es zenen nisht geven demolts keyn TAXIS nokh,

00:07:23.037 --> 00:07:26.728
er zol mikh tsufirn unter der un der numer, un tsu der gas.

00:07:27.777 --> 00:07:31.543
ikh bin arayngekumen, tref ikh dort a khsidishn, yid mit a lange bord,

00:07:32.679 --> 00:07:35.827
zog ikh im, "ikh zukh ayer tokhter Magda."

00:07:36.030 --> 00:07:38.227
zogt er kum nor arayn,

00:07:38.230 --> 00:07:39.289
klapt er,

00:07:42.667 --> 00:07:44.381
zogt mir dey froy, deys meydl,

00:07:44.541 --> 00:07:46.713
kumt aroys a blond meydl dort, zogt zi mir,

00:07:47.433 --> 00:07:50.061
"her mikh tsu," zogt zi,

00:07:50.336 --> 00:07:51.650
"ikh hob bakantshaft," zogt zi,

00:07:52.838 --> 00:07:56.461
"mitn komendant," zogt zi, "un ikh hob a khaverte vos zi iz bakant mitn dokter."

00:07:57.499 --> 00:08:00.370
s'iz a frage, s'iz geven azelkhe militer bikhlekh, vosere

00:08:01.627 --> 00:08:02.770
vosere apteylungen,

00:08:03.021 --> 00:08:04.598
s'iz geven AN un YAN,

00:08:05.330 --> 00:08:08.358
lemoshl AN az me hot bakumen, dem hot men shoyn mer nisht gerufn ober

00:08:08.671 --> 00:08:11.993
efsher iz er geven eyner on a fus, ober un a hant ikh veys,

00:08:12.336 --> 00:08:12.827
zeyer...

00:08:14.016 --> 00:08:21.230
un di YAN, dos iz geven azoy provizorish, host gekent zayn in der heym zeks khadoshim, un nokh dem hostu gekent vider bakumen an aynruf tsetl.

00:08:21.384 --> 00:08:23.403
hob ikh zikh gevolt avade an AN

00:08:23.557 --> 00:08:26.038
zog ikh, "ze tomer kenst erleydikn an AN."

00:08:26.076 --> 00:08:31.557
"UNK azoy vi du kukst oys aza shvere zakh," zogt er, ober tomer CONTROLLED er, ober ikh hob gezogt an AN.

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:42.833
iz aroysgegangen dort, "s'iz nokh mitog da- darfn zey kumen di pritsim, zey forn k- aroys keyn Oroshaza, ikh vel aroysgeyn UNK mit mayn khaverte,

00:08:43.124 --> 00:08:49.249
un ikh vel, zen vos ikh ken ton."

00:08:50.416 --> 00:08:56.187
dertsvishn hob ikh gegan, nisht geganen in keyn hotel arayn voynen, USUALLY gey ikh in, alts in hotel voynen,

00:08:56.333 --> 00:08:58.830
frier hot mir gezogt dort eynem Yakubovitsh,

00:08:58.877 --> 00:09:03.392
vos er hot a restorant, un hot, un er get aroys dort tsimern tsu shlofn oykh dort.

00:09:03.426 --> 00:09:04.569
ikh bin ahin gegangen,

00:09:05.907 --> 00:09:10.449
ikh hob mikh nisht ayngemoldn oykh nisht, se hot geheysn far eyn nakht vos ikh darf dort zayn,

00:09:13.113 --> 00:09:19.284
endlekh iz, nokh mitog,

00:09:19.844 --> 00:09:24.290
ikh bin shoyn gegan ahin, ikh hob gegesn dort mitog, ikh hob mikh tsugeleygt, ikh bin a gantse nakht nisht geshlofn,

00:09:25.307 --> 00:09:28.301
m- zi hot mikh gelozt oyfvekn dort, zogt zi mir, "her mikh tsu," zogt zi,

00:09:29.273 --> 00:09:35.936
men ken ale tsvey erleydikn, eyns kost zibn toyznt doler, der YAN, di andere kost tsen toyznt doler,

00:09:38.736 --> 00:09:40.553
zog ikh, "OKAY," zog ikh, "ikh vel oyfrufn," zog ikh,

00:09:41.318 --> 00:09:42.770
"mayn foter" zog ikh,

00:09:44.827 --> 00:09:47.296
ikh gey telefonirn, un zi shikt mir mit di shvester

00:09:47.981 --> 00:09:48.953
vayzn vi di post iz,

00:09:49.730 --> 00:09:51.318
men hot fun di post ge- telefonirt.

00:09:55.204 --> 00:09:55.936
ikh gey arayn,

00:09:56.484 --> 00:09:59.970
s'iz geven aza tir vos men geyt arayn, azoy vi, vos dreyt zikh azoy.

00:10:00.781 --> 00:10:01.421
ikh gey arayn,

00:10:02.368 --> 00:10:04.902
ikh bet koydem Satmer,

00:10:04.986 --> 00:10:06.650
nokh dem hob ikh gehat a feter vos iz do,

00:10:06.671 --> 00:10:08.507
do geshtorbn far a por yor in Yisroel,

00:10:09.581 --> 00:10:11.296
ikh hob mit im oykh gehat epes tsu redn telefonish,

00:10:13.958 --> 00:10:14.896
un ikh telefonir.

00:10:15.718 --> 00:10:21.330
zogt mir der tate, "zeyer gut, abi men ken erleydikn," ikh hob mit mir mitgenumen epes a elef a halb, tsvelef toyznt PENGO hob ikh gehat mit mir.

00:10:25.087 --> 00:10:27.035
ikh,

00:10:27.898 --> 00:10:34.521
s'iz azoy geven dort ayngefirt az men hot koydem geredt telefonish, un nokh dem iz men tsugegangen tsum fentster un men hot batsolt vifl minut ikh hob geredt azoy fil hob ikh batsolt.

00:10:35.985 --> 00:10:37.333
ikh hob batsolt dort,

00:10:37.449 --> 00:10:39.202
men shraybt oyf dort ver,

00:10:39.463 --> 00:10:42.768
ver, vi azoy der nomen heyst, tsu vemen ikh hob geredt un,

00:10:44.289 --> 00:10:47.058
ikh kum aroys azoy bay di tir, azoy bay di dreyedike tir,

00:10:48.869 --> 00:10:54.076
kumt tsu eyner tsu mir un zogt mir, ", Her Frid!"

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:57.519
ikh bin zeyer dershrokn gevorn, epes a man,

00:10:57.618 --> 00:10:59.204
ver ken mikh do, ver...

00:11:00.050 --> 00:11:02.770
un er makht zikh zofort, vayzt zikh dos knepl, er iz a detektiv.

00:11:03.947 --> 00:11:06.564
zogt er, "ikh heys Andradi, ikh bin a detektiv,

00:11:07.856 --> 00:11:09.810
un kum, undz ze'mir nisht vayt fun do ze'mir,

00:11:10.187 --> 00:11:10.918
hobn mir undzere,

00:11:11.433 --> 00:11:12.827
do der politsey," zogt er,

00:11:14.198 --> 00:11:17.670
"dort vestu, veln mir hern vos du host geredt,

00:11:17.811 --> 00:11:19.647
v- vos du tust do,"

00:11:21.976 --> 00:11:30.670
ikh ze dakht zikh mir az er aylt zikh, azoy demolts ken ikh es makhn kertser, ikh zol es makhn vi kertser?

00:11:32.953 --> 00:11:34.016
zogt er,

00:11:34.496 --> 00:11:36.050
er firt mikh arayn in di politsey arayn,

00:11:38.576 --> 00:11:43.330
un, ikh kum arayn dort ahin, ze ikh s'iz nokh do epes tsvey dray

00:11:43.878 --> 00:11:45.696
andere detektivn, andere dort,

00:11:48.130 --> 00:11:51.730
ikh bin geven on- ongeton azoy sport-mesik, mit aza kapl, veyst ir,

00:11:53.318 --> 00:11:55.307
UNK, tomer darf men aynrukn, ikh veys,

00:11:57.661 --> 00:11:59.604
er heyst mir ikh zol aroysleygn mir dos gelt.

00:12:01.673 --> 00:12:02.484
"leyg aroys dos gelt."

00:12:06.267 --> 00:12:09.776
der detektiv hot gekent tsoln, veys ikh, fir finef hundert PENGO a khoydesh.

00:12:10.873 --> 00:12:13.376
tsvelef toyznt tsu PENGO iz geven zeyer a sakh gelt!

00:12:14.736 --> 00:12:16.450
iber hoypt bay an ayngeshteltn, bay a funktsyonir,

00:12:18.461 --> 00:12:20.918
er geyt un nemt, UNK s'iz geven a groyser tish dort, un

00:12:21.318 --> 00:12:23.833
leygt eyns oyfn andere, di PENGO, hundert PENGO UNK,

00:12:24.781 --> 00:12:27.890
kumt, men kumt un men geyt dort farshidene detektivn, komisarn dort,

00:12:28.667 --> 00:12:32.313
fregt, "vos iz deys a sakh gelt do?" zogt er, "deys iz dem zhidanitse do lebn

00:12:33.593 --> 00:12:34.038
UNK s'iz do."

00:12:37.216 --> 00:12:40.724
"vos tustu do, un vos hos- tustu mitn gelt, un vos hostu telefonirt, vi bistu?

00:12:41.353 --> 00:12:42.221
vu hostu geshlofn?"

00:12:44.758 --> 00:12:46.621
zog ikh, "her mikh tsu, ikh bin gekumen oyf a beshoy,

00:12:47.033 --> 00:12:48.130
ikh bin gekumen onkukn a meydl."

00:12:48.907 --> 00:12:52.187
"vos, mit deys gelt vos tustu, mitn vos vos hostu gedarft brengen gelt?"

00:12:54.816 --> 00:12:59.170
zog ikh, "bayn undz iz a mineg," zog ikh, "az men vert a khosn, koyft men a ringl far far di kale," zog ikh.

00:13:01.009 --> 00:13:03.317
ikh hob nisht gekent epes besers oysklern.

00:13:03.925 --> 00:13:07.460
makht eyner tsum andern koydem hobn zey nisht gegleybt oyf dem meydl

