00:25:17.113 --> 00:25:19.113
ikh bin yede tsvey vokhn aheymgekumen mit UNK,

00:25:19.810 --> 00:25:24.770
dem tatn aheymgebrengt dos gelt, der tate hot nisht gevust mit mir vos tsu ton, er hot mikh gebetn ober UNK makh nisht keyn BUSINESS!

00:25:27.158 --> 00:25:32.404
ikh fleg mamesh, oyfn telefon, fun der heym, ikh hob gevoynt koydem in a in a hotel, ikh hob tsesheydt mit dem yingl,

00:25:32.793 --> 00:25:33.741
der iz gegangen arbetn,

00:25:34.873 --> 00:25:41.170
un funem hotel, ikh fleg onrufn a firme, gekoyft un farkoyft, makhn draysik toyznt, fuftsik toyznt PENGO,

00:25:41.673 --> 00:25:43.696
s'iz gegangen vi vi geshmirt iz ales gegangen.

00:25:44.713 --> 00:25:47.650
ikh hob gehat a gezelshaft mir far- farshaft, khaveyrim dort, ikh fleg

00:25:48.164 --> 00:25:49.901
g- lebn zeyer zeyer gut gelebt.

00:25:50.153 --> 00:25:52.656
ikh hob nisht gevust fun keyn lager fun keyn gornisht v-...

00:25:54.073 --> 00:25:55.341
ikh fleg aheymgekumen yede tsvey vokhn.

00:25:58.336 --> 00:26:00.758
fl- ikh hob gehat a khaver vos iz geven a rayznder oykh mayner,

00:26:01.010 --> 00:26:03.261
er iz geven elter fun mir mit a tsvelef draytsn yor fun mir,

00:26:06.141 --> 00:26:13.284
der, fleg yedn yedn zuntik flegn mir geyn UNK flegn mir geyn in a

00:26:13.638 --> 00:26:15.021
farshidene kafe hoyz,

00:26:17.227 --> 00:26:20.381
fleg mir geyn zikh bodn aza LUKACZ bod iz do dort vos

00:26:21.113 --> 00:26:22.678
se kumt heys vaser fun der erd,

00:26:23.090 --> 00:26:25.558
un se fleg shneyen, un se fleg faln der shney oyf undz,

00:26:25.970 --> 00:26:30.450
un mir flegn mir zikh dort bodn in dem dort in di heyse vaser. iz fleg mir yedn zuntik ahingeyn in a gezelshaft,

00:26:30.747 --> 00:26:32.324
er hot gehat a khaverte oykh, epes a meydl,

00:26:32.598 --> 00:26:34.118
efsher finef zeks mentshn ze'mir ahingegan.

00:26:35.970 --> 00:26:42.233
geven s- a, geven mer koshere restoranen, groyse restoranen, ober ikh hob gegesn bay eynem Shtern, der iz geven der grester dort.

00:26:43.056 --> 00:26:43.764
ikh bin geven a

00:26:45.261 --> 00:26:50.016
a gast vos fleg yedn tog kumen ahin esn, ikh fleg blaybn a mol oyf shabes, ikh bin geven a bakante firme dort.

00:26:50.610 --> 00:26:53.798
men fleg mir telefonirn eyner, men fleg mir gebn, lozn MESSAGES dort bayn im,

00:26:55.558 --> 00:26:59.467
ikh hob gehat geshmuest mit a khaver, er iz oykh geshtorbn do mit a tsvey yor, fun CANADA hot er gevoynt,

00:27:00.107 --> 00:27:02.221
az mir geyn mir, se hot geshpilt a groyse MATCH iz geven,

00:27:03.284 --> 00:27:06.450
az men vet zikh trefn bay Shtern veln mir zikh trefn, un veln mir geyn oyfn MATCH nokh mitog.

00:27:07.318 --> 00:27:07.810
FOOTBALL MATCH.

00:27:10.553 --> 00:27:13.741
ikh kum ahin mitog esn mit dem gantsn oylem maynem, funem bod,

00:27:14.713 --> 00:27:16.976
un ikh gey tsu dem Shtern, er iz geven an elterer yid mit a bord,

00:27:18.450 --> 00:27:20.358
un a zeyer a sheyn elegante gast hoyz,

00:27:21.193 --> 00:27:22.004
ikh gey tsun im tsu,

00:27:22.998 --> 00:27:26.233
un ikh freg im, zog ikh, "MISTER Shtern, men hot mikh nisht gezukht telefonish emetser?"

00:27:28.084 --> 00:27:30.038
zogt er, "ir zent farrikt?" zogt er, "fun vu kumt ir hitst?"

00:27:32.004 --> 00:27:37.158
zogt er, "du veyst nisht az Daytshland hot bazetst yetst der dos d- Budapest dey nakht Pest?"

00:27:39.307 --> 00:27:43.204
ikh bin gekumen funem bod in a halbe UNK, im akhte in der fri avek funem MOTEL, men ho'mir bashtelt a TAXI,

00:27:43.718 --> 00:27:45.570
ze'mir, ikh hob fun gornisht gehert gornisht gevust!

00:27:47.570 --> 00:27:51.387
darf ikh shoyn nisht zogn mit vos far an apetit ikh hob gegesn mitog, vayl s'iz ongekumen mayn khaver, hobn mir zikh

00:27:53.193 --> 00:27:54.804
geshmuest vos zoln mir ton? zoln mir

00:27:55.581 --> 00:28:01.547
kumen, zoln mir geyn tsum MATCH, nisht geyn? zogt er, "geyn vos ken den geshen? loz mir geyn, lomir khotsh a bisl fargesn fun di tsores."

00:28:02.324 --> 00:28:03.193
ikh hob mikh gelozt tsuredn.

00:28:04.347 --> 00:28:07.387
ze'mir gegangen tsum MATCH, aheymkumendik ze'mir shoyn gekumen tsum sh-

00:28:07.417 --> 00:28:10.423
a bisl zikh oyfgezetst oyf a oyf a SUBWAY.

00:28:10.561 --> 00:28:15.284
shoyn nisht geven tsu hobn keyn keyn TAXI dort, men hot shoyn arestirt mentshn oyf di gasn, yidn men hot shoyn legitimirt,

00:28:15.924 --> 00:28:16.884
ze'mir gekumen tsu fus,

00:28:17.536 --> 00:28:19.844
vos zol ikh aykh zogn, ikh hob gehat zeyer a sheyne voynung hob ikh gehat oyf

00:28:20.416 --> 00:28:22.016
un koym hob ikh mikh derzen in der heym

00:28:23.739 --> 00:28:25.024
dos iz shoyn geven ven?

00:28:25.261 --> 00:28:29.421
dos iz geven shoyn nayntsn, nokhn nayntsn nayntsntn un tsvantsikstn,

00:28:29.901 --> 00:28:34.987
in nayntsn, dos UNK dos iz geshen in nayntsn take, nayntsn merts, ven di daytshn zenen arayngekumen UNK

00:28:33.950 --> 00:28:35.240
nayntsn hundert...?

00:28:35.376 --> 00:28:36.244
fir un fertsik.

00:28:40.038 --> 00:28:42.347
endlekh, dem andern tog iz mir ongekumen a shutef mayner,

00:28:42.724 --> 00:28:43.604
mit im bin ikh geven shutfes

00:28:43.958 --> 00:28:47.067
fun Satmer, er hot oykh gehat a mazl, men hot legitimirt in Groysvardayn,

00:28:47.398 --> 00:28:49.341
kumendik keyn Pest, er hot zikh epes aroysgedreyt,

00:28:49.718 --> 00:28:54.313
er iz ongekumen grod tsu mir, er hot gehat a mazl, men hot im nisht arestirt, UNK hot men arestirt bay di ban shoyn di mentshn, dem oylem.

00:28:56.393 --> 00:28:57.010
haklal,

00:28:57.604 --> 00:29:01.364
mir hobn mir geke- gevust fun do ken men zikh shoyn nisht aroysrirn, mir hobn gehat a mazl hobn mir gehat

00:29:01.707 --> 00:29:04.496
unter undz dort iz geven dort a a GROCERY, aza

00:29:04.781 --> 00:29:05.856
DELICATESSEN gesheft,

00:29:06.290 --> 00:29:07.364
ho'mir nisht gegesn nor koshers,

00:29:07.970 --> 00:29:10.290
hobn mir gekent koyfn dort, veys ikh a JAM, honik,

00:29:10.713 --> 00:29:14.987
veys ikh, andere zakhn, un broyt hobn mir gekent bakumen frish broyt, zemelekh tsi vos,

00:29:15.433 --> 00:29:20.016
ho'mir mit dem gelebt, iz gekumen mir ho'mir gehat nokh a khaver, der iz oykh gekumen tsu mir undz zol mir zayn in eynem, zol mir voynen in eynem.

00:29:21.593 --> 00:29:23.821
haklal, ze'mir dort geven in Budapest,

00:29:24.781 --> 00:29:30.096
der tate mayner halt mikh in eyn telefonirn, tsvey dray mol in tog, "kum aheym, kum aheym," zogt er, "vayl di mame iz nishto," zogt er,

00:29:30.438 --> 00:29:31.524
"ikh bin do mit di kinder aleyn.

00:29:31.970 --> 00:29:34.016
loz mikh nisht blaybn aleyn," zogt er, "kum aheym."

00:29:35.604 --> 00:29:37.193
der feter mayner zogt mir

00:29:37.558 --> 00:29:38.793
"gey nisht aheym!" zogt er.

00:29:40.038 --> 00:29:41.216
"Satmer iz a kleyne shtot,

00:29:43.398 --> 00:29:44.427
Satmer iz a kleyne shtot,"

00:29:45.398 --> 00:29:46.793
zogt er, "men vet dikh derkenen," zogt er,

00:29:47.661 --> 00:29:51.924
"do in Pest iz dokh a gresere shtot, du verst farfaln, men ken dikh nisht zeyer do," zogt er,

00:29:52.713 --> 00:29:55.296
"in in a groyser shtot ken men, vert men endersh farfaln a mentsh."

00:29:55.604 --> 00:29:57.901
zogt er, "gey nisht beshum oyfn aheym, khotshik der tate zogt!"

00:29:58.256 --> 00:29:59.193
"er makht dikh umgliklekh!"

00:30:00.404 --> 00:30:05.547
der tate, eyn mol tsvey mol, etlekhe mol telefonirt, "kum aheym, kum aheym." un ikh bin aheymgekumen. undz ho'mir genumen an ofitsir,

00:30:06.233 --> 00:30:11.193
ho'mir gegebn, ikh veys nisht, tsen toyznt PENGO far a gantse, efsher akht nayn mentshn, ze'mir ongekumen oyf keyn Satmer.
